{"tid":2225435,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《巫師3》將推「次世代高畫質」更新版，已擁有玩家可免費升級","createTime":"2020-10-01T10:21:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T03:32:15.000Z","uid":25345,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"8cc08027bf47b9c6917588f9ff250b9db8a9eb20","tid":2225435,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T10:21:03.000Z","msg":"超級良心CDPR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又要重打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nCD Projekt Red 稍早前宣布旗下全球暢銷大作《巫師 3：狂獵》（The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt）為迎接今年即將到來的次世代主機 PS5、Xbox Series X 到來，遊戲推出全面「高畫質完全版」，而已在 PS4、Xbox One 以及 PC 平台擁有遊戲的玩家，將可免費獲得升級更新。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n根據官方公告，全新高畫質版本將會在 PS5、Xbox Series X 獨立販售推出，內容將包含《石之心》、《血與酒》等 DLC 內容，而最重要的是之其在舊平台已購買遊戲的玩家，將可免費升級遊戲至高畫質版。"},{"pid":"b399c0897ebdeb14b4fb0881bec54ddb4c54acd0","tid":2225435,"uid":213841,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T10:22:32.000Z","msg":"又要打多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb30a944e4efbf2a807cf629a23d52bef297d0c","tid":2225435,"uid":169801,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T10:24:17.000Z","msg":"幾時可以升級啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我玩到一半聽到佢話有升級，特登停手，等撚佐半個月啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb4361afc716ed9e8cb115627cadb9fa08ca8f8e","tid":2225435,"uid":25345,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T10:24:32.000Z","msg":"出左5年<br />\n到今日都係冇可超越超級神作<img src=\"/assets/